recent_25_results.question: 5.1 In one sentence, what is the main idea implemented by insertion sort?
recent_25_results.student_answer: 5.1 Takes an element of an array and compares it with the next element, depending on the values of the two elements they will switch and then the program will compare the new switched element with the next one in the array.

recent_25_results.question: 5.1 In one sentence, what is the main idea implemented by insertion sort?
recent_25_results.student_answer: 5.1 Insertion sort divides the list into sorted and unsorted regions, then takes each item from the unsorted region and inserts it into its correct order in the sorted region.

recent_25_results.question: 5.1 In one sentence, what is the main idea implemented by insertion sort?
recent_25_results.student_answer: 5.1 The sorted array or list is built one entry at a time.

recent_25_results.question: 5.1 In one sentence, what is the main idea implemented by insertion sort?
recent_25_results.student_answer: 5.1 It starts with the second element and checks it to see if it is less than the element(s) to the left of it and if it is it inserts it into its corrected position.

recent_25_results.question: 5.1 In one sentence, what is the main idea implemented by insertion sort?
recent_25_results.student_answer: 5.1 Compare two numbers at a time and swap until the entire list is sorted.

recent_25_results.question: 5.1 In one sentence, what is the main idea implemented by insertion sort?
recent_25_results.student_answer: 5.1 Assume the first number is sorted, then move down the list and 'insert' the numbers you come across into the corresponding place on the sorted side of the list.

recent_25_results.question: 5.1 In one sentence, what is the main idea implemented by insertion sort?
recent_25_results.student_answer: 5.1 insertion sort is were after k iterations the first k items in the array are sorted it take the k+1 item and inserts it into the correct position in the already sorted k elements.

recent_25_results.question: 5.1 In one sentence, what is the main idea implemented by insertion sort?
recent_25_results.student_answer: 5.1 Looking at the 2nd element move forward and place the element in the correct spot.
